66
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:08,800
Why is she coming so soon?

67
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,500
Where are your Winged Guards?

68
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:54,000
I can handle you all by myself.

69
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,100
You knew that I'd be coming.

70
00:09:58,100 --> 00:10:00,000
I knew that you'd be coming.

71
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:03,500
And I know why you are here.

72
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:06,700
You annihilated my clan and took away my lover.

73
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:08,900
Of course, you know why.

74
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:20,700
Yi Wuyou, you've been refusing to see the truth

75
00:10:20,700 --> 00:10:22,800
