83
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:25,400
So, please stay here for a while longer.

84
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:27,000
Do it now!

85
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:30,800
Be careful with your weapons.

86
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:32,400
Fan Ruhui.

87
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:34,600
What are you trying to do?

88
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,000
It...

89
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,200
Just wait.

90
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:52,000
Just wait for great things to happen.

91
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,800
Put down the carriage!

92
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,800
Your Majesty.

93
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:24,200
What happened?

94
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,600
There are assassins inside.

95
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,700
Please wait for a moment.

96
00:12:27,700 --> 00:12:29,200
Take me in.

97
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:31,000
Please obey the order.

98
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,200
Who are they?

99
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,900
