105
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:52,100
We agreed to live and die together.

106
00:12:52,100 --> 00:12:54,400
- Open the gate!
- Yes, Your Majesty.

107
00:12:55,300 --> 00:12:56,900
Your Majesty.

108
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:07,500
Do you think I don't know what you did in Tianqi?

109
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:09,500
If it wasn't for me who allowed you to come in,

110
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:12,800
