131
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:18,000
As the emperor, I'll win.

132
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:21,800
And as a man, I'll definitely win.

133
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:23,200
Good.

134
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:27,100
You deserve to be my opponent.

135
