You already knew about Fan Ruhui's plan?

202
00:25:53,710 --> 00:25:55,450
Yes.

203
00:26:00,170 --> 00:26:03,860
Is that why you didn't allow me

204
00:26:03,860 --> 00:26:06,580
to enter Qianyuan Hall today?

205
00:26:07,210 --> 00:26:10,300
But I was the one who made the plan for today.

206
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:12,730
We promised to live together and die together.

207
00:26:12,730 --> 00:26:15,910
He hated me for a long time.

208
00:26:15,910 --> 00:26:18,640
And he'd do anything to kill me.

209
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:21,600
I couldn't put you in danger.

210
00:26:27,990 --> 00:26:30,370
But not everything...

211
00:26:31,260 --> 00:26:36,510
