213
00:26:46,970 --> 00:26:48,970
Yes.

214
00:26:48,970 --> 00:26:53,350
I never thought that he'd acquired an artifact.

215
00:26:53,350 --> 00:26:55,840
But so what?

216
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:59,060
I... still won.

217
00:26:59,060 --> 00:27:02,550
But you are seriously injured.

218
00:27:02,550 --> 00:27:05,780
I have once promised you

219
00:27:05,780 --> 00:27:08,190
that I would accompany you forever

220
00:27:08,190 --> 00:27:10,560
and travel across the Nine States.

221
00:27:10,560 --> 00:27:15,230
But I'm afraid that this time, I'll have to break my promise.

222
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:23,460
Your Majesty, it won't happen.

223
00:27:24,560 --> 00:27:27,670
No one can kill you.

224
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:36,840
I... trusted a lot of people.

225
00:27:36,840 --> 00:27:40,460
And I wanted to share the world with them.

226
00:27:41,090 --> 00:27:43,910
But in the end,

227
00:27:43,910 --> 00:27:46,260
they either wanted to kill me,

228
00:27:46,260 --> 00:27:50,240
or I had no choice but to kill them.

229
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:54,560
I'm... not afraid of death.

230
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:59,570
But I feel a smidgen of regret.

231
00:28:01,400 --> 00:28:04,090
The world is so big.

232
00:28:04,090 --> 00:28:09,520
But there are so few who actually understand me.

233
00:28:14,420 --> 00:28:16,240
Bai Lu,

234
00:28:17,290 --> 00:28:21,060
I know that you are the person

235
00:28:21,060 --> 00:28:22,950
who knows me best in this world.

236
00:28:22,950 --> 00:28:25,810
♫ The mountains are my heart ♫

237
00:28:25,810 --> 00:28:28,426
♫ The rivers are my eyes ♫

238
00:28:28,426 --> 00:28:34,138
♫ And the flora is the peace of my heart ♫

239
00:28:34,138 --> 00:28:37,330
♫ Separated from one another ♫

240
