245
00:28:58,400 --> 00:29:01,330
Your Majesty, even if you will recover tomorrow,

246
00:29:01,330 --> 00:29:03,890
your wound will still hurt today.

247
00:29:03,890 --> 00:29:05,460
Let it hurt then.

