Yes, Your Majesty.

269
00:32:56,860 --> 00:32:58,050
The assets of the Fan Family have been confiscated.

270
00:32:58,050 --> 00:33:00,290
All of the names of the relatives are on this list.

271
00:33:00,290 --> 00:33:05,970
We've confiscated more than 340,000 gold beads and 2,400 pieces of jewelry.

272
00:33:17,540 --> 00:33:19,200
Commander Ling.

273
00:33:21,290 --> 00:33:23,350
First Young Master.

274
00:33:26,360 --> 00:33:30,090
May I ask about my father and brother?

275
00:33:30,090 --> 00:33:32,550
Your father and brother are already dead.

276
00:33:33,620 --> 00:33:35,740
I've been ordered to confiscate the Fan Family's properties.

277
00:33:35,740 --> 00:33:37,730
Please forgive me.

278
00:34:28,230 --> 00:34:33,830
Long live Your Majesty!

279
00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:37,100
You may rise.

280
00:34:37,100 --> 00:34:39,570
Thank you, Your Majesty.

281
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:05,330
I... have married my empress according to the will of God.

282
00:35:05,330 --> 00:35:08,580
We are protected by the gods in the celestial world.

283
00:35:08,580 --> 00:35:13,450
The empress's life star complements mine.

284
00:35:13,450 --> 00:35:19,120
From today onward, we will build the world

285
00:35:19,120 --> 00:35:21,530
and protect it together.

286
00:35:23,370 --> 00:35:30,020
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

287
00:35:33,290 --> 00:35:38,580
The winged man, Yi Wuyou, colluded with Fan Ruhui to commit treason.

288
00:35:38,580 --> 00:35:40,390
Xie Yu'an.

289
00:35:41,090 --> 00:35:43,990
What's the progress of the investigation?

290
00:35:47,010 --> 00:35:53,490
Your Majesty, Xue Xuanjing and Xue Lanwei have already been killed.

291
00:35:53,490 --> 00:35:56,580
Fan Ruhui committed suicide in prison.

292
00:35:56,580 --> 00:36:00,580
And his second son, Fan Zheng, fell off a cliff to his death during a chase.

293
00:36:00,580 --> 00:36:06,420
The eldest son of the Fan Family, Fan Ping, and the eldest grandson, Fan Tianshou, are not involved in this.

294
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,880
They've been demoted to commoners.

295
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:10,170
Okay. I got it.

296
00:36:10,170 --> 00:36:14,270
What's the progress of the construction of the canal?

297
00:36:14,270 --> 00:36:17,560
Official Gu, how long and how much money

298
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:21,430
do you think it'll take to work on the canal?

299
00:36:25,900 --> 00:36:27,730
Your Majesty.

300
00:36:35,700 --> 00:36:38,400
We can start in three months' time.

301
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:40,500
But it'll be winter in three months.

302
00:36:40,500 --> 00:36:42,840
So, the construction will cost more time.

303
00:36:44,600 --> 00:36:46,640
What do you think?

304
00:36:52,430 --> 00:36:55,200
I've always supported the construction of the canal.

305
00:36:55,200 --> 00:36:59,450
We've asked the people of Ningzhou, Wanzhou, and Lanzhou for their labor service before.

306
00:36:59,450 --> 00:37:02,470
And now, Zhongzhou needs people to strengthen the embankment due to the flood.

307
00:37:02,470 --> 00:37:04,680
We don't have enough people to work on this.

308
00:37:04,680 --> 00:37:08,320
Your Majesty, we haven't asked Yuezhou for their labor service this year.

309
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:10,300
We can ask them to do that now.

310
00:37:10,300 --> 00:37:12,610
What do you think?

311
00:37:14,610 --> 00:37:19,170
The people of Yuezhou are quite supportive of the construction of this canal.

312
00:37:19,170 --> 00:37:23,070
I think they are the best choice for this job.

313
00:37:29,610 --> 00:37:33,370
Your Majesty, if the people of my clan can complete this project,

314
00:37:33,370 --> 00:37:35,810
I have a favor to ask.

315
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:40,950
The construction of the canal can help with the flood issue in Zhongzhou.

316
00:37:40,950 --> 00:37:42,660
It'll be an act of kindness.

317
00:37:42,660 --> 00:37:45,860
I hope that you can pardon the people of Yuezhou

318
00:37:45,860 --> 00:37:48,310
who have once gone against you.

319
00:37:48,310 --> 00:37:51,140
Give them the freedom to travel around,

320
00:37:51,140 --> 00:37:55,050
and let them be good citizens of Chao.

321
00:37:58,840 --> 00:38:00,780
That's a great idea.

322
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,980
What you are proposing is the right thing to do.

323
00:38:12,980 --> 00:38:16,930
Of course, I'll pardon them.

324
00:38:18,180 --> 00:38:21,070
We'll do as Her Majesty suggested.

325
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:22,640
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

326
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:36,620
Please have a seat.

327
00:38:43,420 --> 00:38:45,820
Were you looking at the path of the canal?

328
00:38:45,820 --> 00:38:47,430
Yes.

329
00:38:50,370 --> 00:38:53,700
Official Xie, I have something to ask.

330
00:38:53,700 --> 00:38:59,180
Based on my design of the canal, how many people will be living near the canal?

331
00:38:59,990 --> 00:39:01,990
More than 100,000 people I think.

332
00:39:04,330 --> 00:39:05,680
That many?

333
00:39:05,680 --> 00:39:08,790
What is it? Are you planning something?

334
00:39:10,080 --> 00:39:14,920
I want to use the canal as a pathway for business.

335
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:19,800
So, I'm thinking, if it's possible, to ask the people near the canal to become merchants.

336
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:22,120
All of them?

337
00:39:23,750 --> 00:39:27,610
It's really considerate of you to worry about the livelihood of the people.

338
00:39:27,610 --> 00:39:32,280
But it won't be easier than building the canal itself.

339
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:36,010
I... I can't promise anything.

340
00:39:39,530 --> 00:39:44,260
I understand. Please do your best then.

341
00:39:44,260 --> 00:39:45,710
I will.

342
00:39:45,710 --> 00:39:48,800
After the canal is built, I'll do my best to promote this idea.

343
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:51,860
You can plan for it beforehand when you get back to Zhongzhou.

344
00:39:54,270 --> 00:39:56,410
I'll do as you say.

345
00:39:56,410 --> 00:39:59,470
Please accept my thanks.

